.TH "r100_page_flip_pending" 9 "r100_page_flip_pending" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
r100_page_flip_pending \- check if page flip is still pending
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" r100_page_flip_pending
.BI "(struct radeon_device *rdev "  ","
.BI "int crtc_id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rdev" 12
radeon_device pointer
.IP "crtc_id" 12
crtc to check
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Check if the last pagefilp is still pending (r1xx-r4xx).
Returns the current update pending status.
